Ok then just scroll down to the very bottom of this page and click the blue update profile button.

03:30.340 --> 03:37.370
Ok and now that we've made that change if I jumped back to the homemade french bread blog post or any

03:37.370 --> 03:39.040
post for that matter.

03:39.050 --> 03:39.550
Perfect.

