Now let's change gears and learn how to customize our avatar profile photo.

03:52.400 --> 03:58.700
So if I zoom in a bit you can see that currently my profile photo is a cat and you might be wondering

03:58.700 --> 04:01.840
how you can add an Avatar like that to your account.

04:01.850 --> 04:09.050
